00:14:30.440 --> 00:14:31.178
I'm on schedule.

00:14:31.659 --> 00:14:31.740
Ok.

00:14:33.082 --> 00:14:33.719
So, first story.

00:14:34.543 --> 00:14:35.019
Mindset shift.

00:14:36.005 --> 00:14:36.720
I'm losing money.

00:14:37.380 --> 00:14:42.159
Actually, I hadn't even finished losing my minus 20,000 euros

00:14:42.462 --> 00:14:43.539
when I realized I was going to lose money.

00:14:44.346 --> 00:14:45.139
At that moment in the photo.

00:14:46.120 --> 00:14:46.813
Alright?

00:14:47.240 --> 00:14:49.440
At that moment in the photo, as you can see, I look really happy.

00:14:50.861 --> 00:14:53.639
Back then, there was no marchand de biens in France.

00:14:53.941 --> 00:14:55.179
So, I had to get trained abroad.

00:14:55.782 --> 00:14:56.955
Who's read 'Rich Dad Poor Dad'?

00:14:57.860 --> 00:14:57.924
Okay.

00:14:58.320 --> 00:14:59.320
I recommend it to everyone.

00:15:00.385 --> 00:15:01.039
The Cashflow Quadrant.

00:15:01.279 --> 00:15:02.158
I read it, I discovered all this.

00:15:02.600 --> 00:15:03.518
So there I was, in the library.

00:15:04.480 --> 00:15:05.039
I'm at the library.

00:15:05.139 --> 00:15:05.957
