00:15:10.821 --> 00:15:13.759
From 6 to 8, I'd go to the library every day

00:15:14.581 --> 00:15:16.139
to study and take courses.

00:15:16.782 --> 00:15:19.419
And from 8 to 10 PM, since I was single back then,

00:15:22.067 --> 00:15:22.879
I'd hit the gym.

00:15:23.342 --> 00:15:24.240
At 10 PM, I'd get home.

00:15:25.082 --> 00:15:26.340
I'd watch personal development videos.

00:15:26.642 --> 00:15:29.059
I'd keep learning in the bath while eating.

00:15:29.466 --> 00:15:30.000
Never do that.

00:15:31.263 --> 00:15:32.918
I really tried to do three things at once.

00:15:33.200 --> 00:15:33.657
Sometimes it works.

00:15:33.820 --> 00:15:34.399
Sometimes it doesn't.

00:15:34.559 --> 00:15:35.039
It's not great.

00:15:35.179 --> 00:15:35.960
I looked into it afterwards.

00:15:37.159 --> 00:15:37.960
So, you get the idea.

00:15:38.139 --> 00:15:38.938
I was getting into it.

00:15:39.360 --> 00:15:41.559
And then, I started cooking.

00:15:41.823 --> 00:15:42.779
